 Edit an Output Node in a Batch Data Transform

Add a column to a data model object (DMO) output node without leaving the editor. Previously, to change a DMO, you needed to leave the batch data transform and go to the Data Model Objects tab to add a column.

Where: This change applies to Data Cloud in Developer, Enterprise, Performance, and Unlimited editions.

When: This feature is available starting in June 2024.

How: In a batch data transform, click an output node. From the list of available columns, click Create New.
